A quicker delivery on leg. Jadeja works it towards deep square leg for a single.
Tossed up around off. Shami defends this off the front foot.
Another rock-solid defence by Shami! Tossed up nicely on off and equally nicely defended off the front foot by Shami.
Tossed up delivery, on off. Jadeja blocks this off the front foot.
Beaten this time! Tossed up on middle and there is turn and bounce for Dhananjaya de Silva. It beats the outside edge of Jadeja's blade as he looks to defend.
Another flighted delivery on off. Jadeja defends it towards the off side.
Tad short this time and turning away. It is around off and Jadeja punches it to sweeper cover for a single.
Loopy delivery around off. Shami pushes it to covers.
This time a bit quicker on off. Shami blocks this off the front foot.
Tossed up on middle. Jadeja blocks this off the front foot.
SIX! Great use of the feet there! A tossed up delivery on middle. Jadeja skips down the track and tonks it straight down the ground for a maximum.

FOUR! Lasith Embuldeniya overcompensates and serves this short around leg. Jadeja pulls it to backward square leg. The fielder in the deep runs to his left and tries to stop it with a dive but it goes through him for a boundary. 500 up for India!
FOUR! Another poor delivery and punished by Jadeja! This is slightly short and down the leg side again. Jadeja pulls it towards backward square leg for another boundary.
A flatter delivery on middle. Jadeja works it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Quicker and flatter delivery on off. Shami defends it back to the bowler.
On a length, around off. Jadeja gets a thick outside edge this time as he looks to defend it. The ball goes towards the gully fielder.
A fullish delivery on off. Jadeja drives it to mid on.
A low full toss on middle. Jadeja flicks it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
NO BALL! Lakmal bangs this one short on off. Jadeja pulls it to deep mid-wicket for a single this time. Lakmal has overstepped and the umpire calls it a no ball.

NOT OUT! FOUR LEG BYES! A length delivery on middle and leg. Shami looks to work it towards the leg side but misses. The ball hits his pads and there is a big appeal. The umpire though is not interested. The ball goes towards the off side and the fielder at gully has a shy at the batter's end but misses and the ball goes towards the fence for a boundary as there is no one backing up. In the meanwhile, Sri Lanka have taken a review for LBW. The replays roll in and the UltraEdge shows no bat involved. The Ball Tracker rolls and it shows umpire's call on wickets hitting. So Shami will continue and India get four leg byes.
A fuller delivery on middle. Shami blocks it out.
A full toss this time on middle. Shami plays it down to mid on.
Loopy ball, full, on middle. Ravindra Jadeja lunges and defends it out.
Tosses it up nicely, very full, around off. Ravindra Jadeja pushes it towards mid off.
Slower through the air, full once again, on middle. Ravindra Jadeja leans and defends it out watchfully.
Loopy ball, around off. Ravindra Jadeja hangs back and pushes it towards cover.

Full again, on middle. Ravindra Jadeja stays in his crease and pushes it on the left of the bowler. Mohammed Shamiwanted a single there, but Ravindra Jadeja says no. Dhananjaya de Silva does well to run to his left and cut the ball out.
No ball and Four! Shorter ball again, around middle. Ravindra Jadeja hangs back and pulls it over mid-wicket for a boundary. Dhananjaya de Silva has overstepped here and a no ball is called.
SIX! Ravindra Jadeja brings up his 150 in style! A loopy ball, fuller and around off. Ravindra Jadeja dances down the track and tonks it over long off for a biggie!
A length delivery, on off. Shami blocks it out.
Mohammed Shami gets off the mark on his 15th delivery! Length ball, around middle and leg. Mohammed Shami flicks it to fine leg for a single.
Fuller now, spraying it down leg. Ravindra Jadeja clips it towards square leg. No run taken!
Another fuller ball, outside off. Ravindra Jadeja drives it straight to the fielder at deep cover. Another do ball.
Suranga Lakmal drops it short now, around middle. Ravindra Jadeja pulls it towards deep square leg. This time Ravindra Jadeja rotates the strike.
Another back-of-a-length delivery, around middle. Mohammed Shami pulls it towards fine leg. No run taken!
On a length, outside off. Ravindra Jadeja stays back, opens the face of the bat, and guides it towards third man for a brace.

A mix-up...and no harm done! A run out chance but Sri Lanka make a mess of it! An easy opportunity for Sri Lanka. A length ball, around middle. Ravindra Jadeja taps it towards mid-wicket. They run the first one fast, Mohammed Shami comes back for the second, but he is sent back by Ravindra Jadeja mid-way. The fielder though throws it at the wrong end, towards the bowler. Vishwa Fernando too collects the ball and whips the bails off, of the non-striker's end, he did not realize that Shami was well out of his crease. A comedy of errors.
FOUR! Mohammed Shami adds salt to the wound! A fuller ball, wide of off. Mohammed Shami leans and drives it past cover for a beautiful boundary.
A good-length delivery, around off. Shami drives it to mid off.
On a length, around off. Shami pushes it towards point and takes a single.
FOUR! A boundary to end the over! Vishwa Fernando drops it short, around middle. Ravindra Jadeja picks up the length, and pulls it towards deep mid-wicket for a boundary.
Loopy ball, fuller, on middle. Mohammed Shami blocks it out.
Tad shorter, an arm ball, around the pads. Mohammed Shami looks to flick this, but he the ball goes off the outside edge towards point. A single taken!
Down the leg side, touch shorter, Ravindra Jadeja gets low and sweeps it towards deep square leg for a single.
Quicker and flatter, on middle. Mohammed Shami hangs back and blocks it out.
FOUR! Cut away! Lasith Embuldeniya drops it slightly short, spinning away, outside off. Mohammed Shami slashes it past cover for a boundary.
Touch shorter again, on middle. Mohammed Shami punches it down to long on. Mohammed Shami denies a single a this time.
On a length, outside off. Ravindra Jadeja taps it towards point for a single.
Good-length delivery, on middle. Mohammed Shami defends it out solidly.
Tad fuller now, outside off. Mohammed Shami drives and finds the fielder at cover.
Angling in, on middle. Mohammed Shami tucks it to mid-wicket.

Another length delivery, outside off. Mohammed Shami guides it towards cover. The fielder from point slides to stop the ball but fails, another fielder from cover runs for the ball, but he too fails to get hold of the ball. Two taken!
Fuller, around off. Mohammed Shami pushes taps it to mid-off.

FOUR BYES! Nothing is going Sri Lanka's way here! A fuller ball, down the leg side. Ravindra Jadeja looks to sweep but he misses. Niroshan Dickwella too fails to grab the ball, as it sneaks in through his legs towards fine leg for a boundary.
Tosses it up, on middle. Ravindra Jadeja leans and defends it out.
SIX! Bang! Another fuller ball, around middle. Ravindra Jadeja shimmies down the track and smashes it over long on for a biggie!
Loopy ball, very full, around middle and leg. Ravindra Jadeja tucks it towards square leg for a brace.
Flatter ball now, full in length, around middle. Ravindra Jadeja knocks it to long on for a single.
TWO LEG BYES! Shorter now, around the pads. Mohammed Shami tries to flick this, but the ball brushes off his pads towards fine leg. Two taken!
On a length, around middle and leg. Ravindra Jadeja works it away towards mid-wicket for a single.
FOUR! Edgy runs! Tad fuller, wide of off. Mohammed Shami leans to drive but the ball goes off the outside edge past the second slip fielder for a boundary.
Another length ball, around off. Mohammed Shami looks to push this away but gets an inside edge towards fine leg for a single.
Change of pace now! A slower one, angling in on middle, on a length. Ravindra Jadeja eases it to long for a single.

Back of a length, outside off. Mohammed Shami taps it to point and scampers through to the other end. There is a throw at the non-striker's end, but the ball hits Shami on the back. That brings up the 100 run partnership between these two!
Fuller ball, outside off. Ravindra Jadeja tries to go over cover, but the ball goes off the outer half of the bat towards point. Single taken!
A flatter delivery around leg. Jadeja pulls it to backward square leg for a single.
Shorter delivery on middle. Shami punches it to long on for a single.  Meanwhile, Rohit Sharma calls his batters in and India declare! India finish with 574/8 in their first innings!

FOUR! Dimuth Karunaratne and Sri Lanka are underway with a boundary! Positive start from the Lankan skipper. A length delivery drifting on middle and leg. Dimuth Karunaratne flicks it through mid-wicket for a boundary.

NO BALL! There is an huge appeal but the umpire turns it down. However, Shami has overstepped and it is anyways a no ball. It is a length delivery on middle and leg again. This time it skids through and beats Dimuth Karunaratne as he looks to defend but the ball hits his pads.
On a length and around off. Dimuth Karunaratne dabs it towards the off side for a single.
A good-length delivery on middle and Lahiru Thirimanne goes back and blocks it towards the leg side.
Another delivery that is angled into the left-hander. It is on a length and Lahiru Thirimanne goes back and blocks it.
A fullish delivery around off. Lahiru Thirimanne blocks this off the front foot.
A length delivery to end the over. It is again on the off stump line and Lahiru Thirimanne blocks it out.
Jasprit Bumrah begins with a length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne taps it towards cover for a single.
Fuller now, down the leg side. Lahiru Thirimanne misses his flick.
Back of a length, around off. Lahiru Thirimanne stays in his crease and blocks it out.
Fuller now, spraying it on the pads. Lahiru Thirimanne clips it to fine leg for a single.
Fuller now, outside of, at 139.2 clicks. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it to mid off.
Good ball to end the over! Length ball, shaping away, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leaves it alone.
FOUR! Second over from Shami and it also starts with a boundary! A fullish delivery on off. Lahiru Thirimanne leans forward and drives it past mid off for a lovely boundary.

Overthrows this time! A length delivery, on off. Lahiru Thirimanne defends it towards covers and Iyer runs forward and has a shy at the bowler's end. There is no one backing up and that gives away two extra runs to Lahiru Thirimanne.
A length delivery, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne defends it towards mid on.
This time on a good length and outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne leaves it alone.
Another good-length delivery and outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne lets it go comfortably yet again.
A good-length delivery and this time it is near the off pole. Lahiru Thirimanne blocks it out.
Back of a length, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne rides the bounce and defends this with the bottom of his blade onto the pitch. This one keeps a tad low.
A good-length delivery, outside off and shaping away this time. Dimuth Karunaratne leaves it alone.
He attacks the stumps this time and serves this on good length, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it solidly.
Bangs this one short, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne lets it go easily.
Another short delivery around off. It is 133.4 kph. This time Dimuth Karunaratne tries to pull it but misses.
FOUR! Another lovely shot by Dimuth Karunaratne! Overpitched on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne leans forward and flicks it through covers for a boundary. Sri Lanka are off to a good start!
A flatter delivery and quicker on off. Lahiru Thirimanne defends it towards point.
This time slower in the air, on off.  Lahiru Thirimanne defends it off the front foot.
On middle and leg. Lahiru Thirimanne works it towards backward square leg for a single.
This one pitches on middle and there is a hint of away turn there. Dimuth Karunaratne gets forward and defends it nicely though.
Quicker and drifting on the pads now. Dimuth Karunaratne works it to deep square leg for a couple.
Flatter and quicker outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne cuts it to point.
Back of a length, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne works it towards mid-wicket.
A bit fuller this time, on off. Lahiru Thirimanne defends it solidly towards the leg side.

A length delivery angling into middle and leg from 'round the wicket. Lahiru Thirimanne looks to work it towards the leg side but misses. The ball hits his pads and a leg bye is taken towards fine leg.

This one was in the air for a brief period but quite safe! Back of a length, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to defend, however, the ball hits him high on the bat and the ball goes towards mid on slightly aerially.
Another length delivery angled into middle and leg now. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out.
A short ball on middle to end the over. Dimuth Karunaratne ducks under it.
A flatter delivery on off. Lahiru Thirimanne goes forward and blocks it out.
Tad fuller this time on off. Lahiru Thirimanne drives it to mid off.
This one is bit slower and fuller on off. Lahiru Thirimanne drives it little uppishly towards the off side.
Another tossed up delivery, on off. Lahiru Thirimanne drives it to mid off again.
He is getting into his strides now. Bowls this slower again, around off. Lahiru Thirimanne drives it off the outside half of his blade to point.
Flatter and quicker on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne blocks this off the front foot.
Back of a length, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out off the back foot.
A length delivery, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne works it towards a squarer mid-wicket.
Angled into middle and slightly fuller this time. Dimuth Karunaratne drives this off the inside half of his blade towards the leg side.
Bumrah is targeting those stumps regularly. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to clip it but the ball hits his thigh.
A full toss this time, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it back to the bowler.
This time he goes fuller on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne flicks it to deep mid-wicket for a couple.
Tossed up nicely on off. Lahiru Thirimanne drives it towards mid off.
Ohh...turn and bounce! Tossed up delivery, around of and turning away. Lahiru Thirimanne looks to push at it but gets beaten.
Slower again, on off. Lahiru Thirimanne blocks it out.
Goes slightly quicker and fuller on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne drives it to mid off.
Fuller again, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne knocks it back to Ashwin.
Nicely bowled again by Ashwin! This is slower in the air, around off. Lahiru Thirimanne pushes forward to defend but the ball turns away and beats him off the outside edge.
A quicker delivery on off to start by Yadav. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks this off the front foot.
Slower this time and around off. Dimuth Karunaratne gets well forward and defends it.
A flatter delivery on off. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out.
Flighted delivery on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne skips down the track and ends up defending it as he fails to recah the pitch of the ball.
A slider this time on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out off the front foot.
This time he serves this wider and slower outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it to the short cover fielder.
Quicker and flatter, around middle and leg. Lahiru Thirimanne taps it towards mid-wicket.
Loopy ball now, fuller, outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne leans and efends it out.
Shorter now, turning away, outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne cuts it past point for a single.
Beauty! Slower through the air, tosses it up, full and turning away, outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne looks to heave this over the leg side but misses and the ball spins away sharply.
Fuller again, outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne blocks it out.
Slower again, loopy ball, outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne looks to slash this but gets an inside edge onto the deck.
Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne punches it off the back foot towards cover for a single.
Short again, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne tucks it to mid-wicket for a single.
Fuller this time, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leans and blocks it out.
Tosses it up, full, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it back to the bowler.
Very full, on the toes this time. Dimuth Karunaratne works it away towards mid-wicket.
Slower through the air, fuller ball, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne shows the full face of the bat and blocks it out off the front foot.
Flighted delivery, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne presses forward and defends it out.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Lahiru Thirimanne taps it towards silly point off the back foot.
Tosses it up, yorker-length delivery, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne digs it out.
Shorter ball, turning away, outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne stays back and looks to cut this away, but the gets an inside edge onto the pads of the keeper.
Fuller ball, outside off, spinning away. Lahiru Thirimanne leans to drive, but he manages to get an outside edge past the first slip fielder for two runs.
Tad shorter, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne flicks it towards square leg for a single.
Much quicker this time, on middle, full in length. Lahiru Thirimanne tries to block but the ball goes off the inside edge on the leg side.
Fuller, loopy ball, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne leans and defends it out.
FOUR! Some aggression shown by Dimuth Karunaratne! A loopy ball again, fuller, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne shimmies down the track and lifts it over the bowler's head for a boundary.
NO BALL AND FOUR! Another fuller ball, no turn there. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it past mid on for a boundary. Jayant Yadav has overstepped here and a no ball is called!
Fuller ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out.
On middle, fuller ball. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out.
Quicker now, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne misses his flick and gets rapped on the pads.
Slower through the air, loopy ball, outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne waits for it and drives it past cover for a brace.
Full again, tosses it up, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne presses forward and defends it out.
Loopy ball, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne looks to flick this on the leg side, but teh ball goes off the outside edge past the slip fielder.
Tad shorter, around off. Lahiru Thirimanne taps it towards point.
Full again, flighted ball, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne leans and defends it out.
Another loopy ball, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne lunges and blocks it out.
Quicker this time, firing it on the pads. Dimuth Karunaratne stays back and flicks it towards square leg.
Slower now, on the pads again. Dimuth Karunaratne leans and looks to defend this but misses and gets rapped on the front pad.
Slower through the air, full, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne lunges and taps it towards point.
Full again, loopy ball, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out watchfully.
Much quicker this time, full, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it to the fielder at cover.
Loopy ball, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it back to the bowler.
Slower through the air, on middle, pitches it up. Lahiru Thirimanne presses forward and defends it out.
Loopy ball, around middle and leg. Lahiru Thirimanne leans and tucks towards square leg for a single.
Tosses it up, fuller in length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne lunges and blocks it out solidly.
Another flighted delivery, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends this one.
Floated delivery, full in length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leans and to defend this but the ball goes off the outside edge past the silly point fielder.
FOUR! Classy! Ravichandran Ashwin overpitches this one, wide of off, Dimuth Karunaratne leans and drives it past extra-cover for a glorious boundary.
Tosses it up, on middle, full in length. Lahiru Thirimanne presses forward and blocks it out soidly.
Full again, loopy ball, outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne defends it out.
Shorter now, spinning away, outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne cuts it towards point.
Flighted ball, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne has blocked this one.
On a length, around middle and leg. Lahiru Thirimanne flicks it towards mid-wicket for a single.
No ball! Full again, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks this one. Jayant Yadav have overstepped again and the umpire calls it a no ball.
Loopy ball, on middle, Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it back to the bowler.
Very full, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne works it away towards mid on.

OUT! LBW! Ravichandran Ashwin strikes and draws first blood! He breaks the opening partnership and India get their first wicket! A loopy ball, this one keeps sliding in with the arm. Lahiru Thirimanne leans to defend this, but he gets beaten and the ball sneaks past his inside edge and hits him on the front pad. A huge appeal for LBW, and the umpire raises his finger! Lahiru Thirimanne decides to go for the review. No bat involved confirms UltraEdge and three reds shows Ball Tracker. Lahiru Thirimanne has to walk back.
Howout: lbw b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: Fuller ball, around off. Pathum Nissanka leans and defends it out.
Another fuller ball, around off, loopy delivery. Pathum Nissanka pushes it towards mid on.

Ohh...almost a wicket again! A slower delivery around off with a hint of turn into the batter. Nissanka looks to defend but the ball catches the inside edge of his blade. It goes past stumps and the leg slip fielder for a couple.
Tossed up nicely on off. Nissanka gets well forward and blocks it out.
Angling in, around off, on a length. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to push this away from his body but he manages to get an inside edge on his pads.
Good-length delivery, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne taps it towards point.
Another length delivery, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne once again tries to push this on the off side, but he gets an inside edge onto his pads.
Angling in, on a length, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives and finds the fielder at mid off.
Jagging back in on middle, on a length, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne taps it towards mid on.
Tad shorter, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne dabs it towards backward point.
Tossed up delivery on off. Nissanka drives it to mid on.
Flatter and shorter on off and turning into Nissanka. He goes back and plays it back to the bowler.
This one goes straight! A fuller delivery, outside off. Nissanka looks to defend but gets beaten off the outside edge.
A fuller delivery, outside off. Nissanka pushes it towards the off side.
On middle and leg this time. Nissanka works it towards the leg side.
Another loppy delivery on off. Nissanka defends this off the front foot.

Ohh...Indian players went off for an appeal but realised soon that it is going down leg. A fuller delivery angling into middle and leg. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to flick it but misses. The ball hits his pads and there is an appeal  but going down leg.

Inside edge this time! A length delivery and tailing into the batter. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to defend but gets the inside edge onto his pads and the ball loops in the air towards the leg side but falls short of the short mid-wicket fielder.
This is shorter and down the leg side. Dimuth Karunaratne lets it go. Pant dives to his right and makes a good stop.
On the pads this time. Dimuth Karunaratne flicks it to square leg.
Shami goes over the wicket and serves this down the leg side. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to glance it away but misses.
A fullish delivery on off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it to covers.
This is a loopy delivery again on middle. Nissanka goes back to a fuller delivery and ends up getting under edge onto his pads.
Ohh...just away from the short leg fielder now! Nicely tossed up on middle. Nissanka defends but gets the inside edge of his blade and just past the short leg fielder.
FOUR! He decides to use his feet now and gets a boundary! Tossed up on middle. Nissanka skips down the track and heaves it towards deep mid-wicket for a boundary.
Slightly shorter on middle. Nissanka goes back and blocks it out.
Another loopy delivery on off. Nissanka defends it with soft hands towards the off side.
Tossed up delivery and slower through the air, on off. Nissanka is well forward to block it.
FOUR LEG BYES! This time drifting on the pads. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to tuck it away but misses. The ball brushes his thigh and goes away towards the long leg fence for a boundary.
On a length, angling into middle now. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out.

Bit of reverse swing there! A good-length delivery, around off and tailing away slightly. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to defend but the ball catches the outside edge of his blade towards Vihari at second slip.
A fullish delivery on off. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it to mid off and takes a single.
A good-length delivery on off. Nissanka blocks it out towards the off side.
It is reversing now!  Goes a tad fuller this time on off and a bit of away shape there. Nissanka defends but the ball goes off the outer half of his blade towards the off side.

Huge appeal but the umpire turns it down! A tossed up delivery around off and turning into Dimuth Karunaratne. He looks to slog-sweep it but misses. The ball hits his back leg and there is an appeal but the umpire turns it down. Indian players have a discussion and they decide to not review it.

OUT! LBW! This time he gets his man! What a delivery again by Jadeja and huge turn for the left-arm spinner straightaway! He serves this around off and around that rough again. The ball turns into the batter sharply again and Dimuth Karunaratne is stuck on his crease as he looks to defend it. The ball hits his pads and there is an appeal. The umpire raises his finger this time. Dimuth Karunaratne reviews it straightaway. The UltraEdge confirms no bat involved. The Ball Tracker rolls and it shows the umpire's call on impact. So the original decision stays and Dimuth Karunaratne has to walk back. Ravindra Jadeja strikes in his first over! He is displaying his magic with the ball as well!
Howout: lbw b Ravindra Jadeja

Commentary: NO BALL! Turn again! A tossed up delivery, around off.  Angelo Mathews pushes forward to defend but gets a thick outside edge and the ball falls just short of gully there. However, Jadeja has overstepped and it is a no ball anyway.
A flatter delivery on middle. Mathews works it towards the leg side this time.
Darted on middle and leg this time. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards deep square leg and gets three runs here.
Tossed up on off. Nissanka gets forward and blocks it out.
Slightly shorter on off. Nissanka backs away and punches it to covers.
Yorker-length delivery, on middle. Angelo Mathews squeezes it out towards the leg side.
On a length, around off. Angelo Mathews defends it out.
Angling in on the pads, at 132.2 clicks, on a length. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards square leg.
Back of a length, outside off, at 142.4 clicks. Angelo Mathews hops and blocks it out.
Leg bye! Angling in the pads, on a length. Angelo Mathews looks to flick this on the le side, but the ball brushes off his pads and rolls towards fine leg. Leg bye taken!
FOUR! top shot! Fuller now, outside off. Pathum Nissanka presses forward and drives it past cover for a boundary.
Loopy ball, outside off. Angelo Mathews cuts it towards point. Ravindra Jadeja has overstepped her and a no ball is called!
Shorter, outside off, turning it away, this one stays low as well. Angelo Mathews pushes it past cover for a brace.
Quicker, spinning away, outside off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out off the back foot.
Short again, outside off. Angelo Mathews knocks it towards cover.

An appeal for LBW, but the umpire says no! This one slides in with the arm, much fuller in length. Angelo Mathews leans to defend but misses and gets rapped on the pads. That was sliding down leg. Good decision.
Much fuller again, outside off. Angelo Mathews leans and defends it out.
FOUR! Nicely done! Full again, on middle. Angelo Mathews steps down and lifts it over mid on for a boundary.
Angling in on the pads, on a length. Pathum Nissanka tucks it to square leg.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Pathum Nissanka defends it out.
A flatter delivery on middle. Nissanka blocks it out off the back foot.
Swinging in, on a length, on middle. Pathum Nissanka pushes it back towards mid on.
Tad fuller, on middle. Pathum Nissanka gets behind the line and defends it out.
On a length, around off. Pathum Nissanka pushes it back to the bowler.
Loopy ball, very full, on middle. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Tad shorter, around middle. Angelo Mathews pushes it back to Jadeja.
Quicker now, spinning away, around middle. Angelo Mathews stays back and defends it out.
Loopy ball, very full, on middle. Angelo Mathews leans and blocks it out watchfully.
Tosses it up, on middle, full in length. Angelo Mathews presses forward and defends it out.
Another flighted delivery, pitching it up, around off. Angelo Mathews lunges and defends it out. A maiden for Ravindra Jadeja!
On a length, on middle. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out solidly.
FOUR! Edgy runs! Another length delivery, outside off. Pathum Nissanka looks to defend this, but the ball goes off the outside edge towards third man for a boundary.
Angling in, on middle. Pathum Nissanka tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Tad fuller, coming back in, on middle. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out solidly.
Yorker-length delivery, on middle. Pathum Nissanka digs it out.
Full again, on middle. Pathum Nissanka shows the full face of the bat and defends it out.
A flatter delivery, on middle. Angelo Mathews goes back and blocks it out.
NO BALL! This is fuller on middle. Angelo Mathews defends this off the front foot. However, Jadeja has overstepped again and it is a no ball.
A fuller delivery on middle. Angelo Mathews drives it to mid on.
A flatter delivery and quciker again, on off. Angelo Mathews defends it from his crease.
Pushed quicker again on off. Angelo Mathews defends it out again.
This is slightly slower on off. Angelo Mathews gets forward and blocks it out.
Tossed up nicely this time, on off. Angelo Mathews gets his front foot forward and blocks it.
Back of a length, on off. Nissanka is solid in his back foot defence here.
Nice bounce there for Bumrah! Back of a length, on off. Nissanka rides the bounce and the ball hits Nissanka on his glove as he tries to defend it.

NO BALL! Ohh...this time a no ball has cost India! A good-length delivery, slower this time, around off. Nissanka pushes forward to defend but the ball nips in and shatters his stumps. Bumrah and Indian players start celebrating but the siren rings and it signals a no ball. Lucky reprieve for Nissanka and Bumrah is disappointed.
A yorker this time, outside off. Nissanka looks to dig it out but misses.
This time a pacy bouncer on off. Nissanka tries to defend it but the ball hits his gloves and goes off towards the third man region for a couple.
A slower full ball this time, outside off at 116.1 kph. Nissanka looks to drive but gets beaten.
Wow! Now a yorker on middle over 140 clicks! Nissanka manages to dig it out. Superb over from Bumrah!
SIX! Angelo Mathews breaks the shackles this time! Tossed up on off. Angelo Mathews takes a good stride forward and lofts this straight down the ground for a maximum.
Drags his length back this time, on off. Angelo Mathews goes back and punches it through covers for a couple.
Quicker at 89.6 kph, on off. Angelo Mathews defends this off the front foot.
This time even quicker and slightly shorter on middle at 95.6 kph. Angelo Mathews works it towards deep mid-wicket for a couple.
On middle and leg. Angelo Mathews plays it awkwardly this time behind square on the leg side for a single.
Sharp turn this time! On off and Nissanka presses forward to defend. However, the ball turns away sharply and beats the outside edge of his blade.
A good-length delivery, around off at 139.3 kph. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
A good-length delivery shaping into the batter this time. It is pitches outside off and Angelo Mathews leaves it alone.
Goes for a yorker this time, Bumrah! He bowls this on middle at 144.6 kph. Angelo Mathews digs it out towards mid-wicket for a couple.
Now a slower delivery, on off. A length delivery this and Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Beats him this time! A good-length delivery, around off and shaping away a tad this time. Angelo Mathews pushes for it but gets beaten.

OUT! LBW! Angelo Mathews departs and Bumrah is finally rewarded for his superb spell here! He gets the big fish, Angelo Mathews now and Sri Lanka lose their third wicket now. A good-length delivery, on off and Angelo Mathews is not sure which way it is going and gets beaten as he looks to defend. The ball hits his pads and there is an appeal. The umpire raises his finger and  Angelo Mathews reviews it. The UltraEdge confirms no bat involved. The Ball Tracker rolls and it shows umpire's call on impact and wickets hitting. So Angelo Mathews has to walk back and this is a big blow to Sri Lanka.
Howout: lbw b Jasprit Bumrah

Commentary: FOUR! Shorter ball, wide of off. Pathum Nissanka stays back and slashes it past point for a boundary.
Fuller ball, on middle. Pathum Nissanka leans and defends it out.
Another tossed up ball, full, around off. Pathum Nissanka presses forward and defends it out solidly.
Loopy ball, fuller in length, around off. Pathum Nissanka lunges and blocks it out watchfully.
Turn and bounce! Quicker, full, turning it away, around off. Pathum Nissanka leans and looks to defend this but he does so with his gloves due to the extra bounce.
A fullish delivery on off. Nissanka drives it to the short cover fielder.
Fuller delivery and drifting on the pads. Dhananjaya de Silva works it towards fine leg for a single.
A fullish delivery, on off. Nissanka blocks this off the front foot.
A short delivery this time, around off. Nissanka sways away from the line of the ball.
It is reversing for Bumrah now! A good-length delivery that pitches around off and tails into Nissanka. He blocks it out.
A good-length delivery, on middle. Nissanka blocks it out towards the leg side.
A good-length delivery, around off. Nissanka opens the face of his blade towards backward point for a couple.
A tossed up delivery, around off. Dhananjaya de Silva defends but gets a thick outside edge wide of second slip.
A flatter delivery on middle. Dhananjaya de Silva works it towards the leg side.
Another quicker delivery on off. Dhananjaya de Silva blocks it out this time.
Pushed quicker on off. Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it towards point as he opens the face of his blade a little.
Quicker and flatter on off. Dhananjaya de Silva defends this off the front foot solidly.
Again that flatter trajectory on off. Dhananjaya de Silva defends it out.
Angling in on middle, on a length, at 141.1 clicks. Pathum Nissanka defends it out.
Swinging it in again, around off, on a length, at 143 clicks. Pathum Nissanka taps it towards point.
Jasprit Bumrah misses his length, serves a full toss, on middle, slower ball. Pathum Nissanka pushes it back to the bowler.
Full now, outside off, at 141.8 kph. Pathum Nissanka lunges and blocks it out.
Jasprit Bumrah drops it short now, around middle. Pathum Nissanka ducks underneath it.
Another shorter ball, around middle. Pathum Nissanka taps it towards mid-wicket. A maiden for Jasprit Bumrah!

OUT! LBW! Change of bowling has worked! Ravichandran Ashwin comes into the attack and strikes! Sri Lanka lose their fourth and Ravichandran Ashwin picks up his second. Very full, lower through the air, turning in just a tad. Dhananjaya de Silva gets down on his knee and tries to sweep this, but gets beaten as the ball comes in just a bit and hits him on the front pad. They appeal for LBW, and the umpire raises his finger! Dhananjaya de Silva decides not to take the review and he walks back!
Howout: lbw b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: Fuller ball, outside off. Charith Asalanka leans defends it out.
Loopy again, full, around off. Charith Asalanka lunges and blocks it out.
Slower through teh air, full in length, outside off. Charith Asalanka presses forward and defends this one.
Pitches it up again, outside off. Charith Asalanka drives it past cover for a single. He gets off the mark.
Full again, on middle. Pathum Nissanka knocks it to long on for a single.
Fuller ball, on middle. Pathum Nissanka lunges and defends it out.
Quicker ball, at 91,1 clicks, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out solidly.
Another fuller ball, turning it away, outside off. Pathum Nissanka clears his front foot and pushes it past point for a brace.
Shorter now, around middle. Pathum Nissanka pushes it towards mid-wicket for a single.

NOT OUT! A fuller ball, spinning in, on middle. Charith Asalanka leans to block this, but misses, and he gets rapped on the front pad. The umpire raises his finger after a huge shout by the Indians. Charith Asalanka opts for a review. No bat involved confirms UltraEdge. Ball TRacker shows the ball would have missed the wickets. The decision needs to be overturned!
Another comes in, around middle fuller ball. Blocked out.
Fuller and slower in the air on leg. Nissanka defends it towards the leg side.
Another loopy delivery on middle. Nissanka gets well forward and blocks it.
Loopy ball, on middle. Pathum Nissanka leans defends it out.
Ravichandran Ashwin goes over the wicket now, serves a fuller ball, on middle. Pathum Nissanka defends it out.
This one slides in with the arm, on middle. Pathum Nissanka defends it out off the front foot.
Quicker now, around middle. Pathum Nissanka blocks it off the back foot this time.
Fuller ball, on middle. Charith Asalanka leans and defends this one.
An appeal for LBW, but turned down! Much straighter this time, on middle. Charith Asalanka leans to blocks this but misses and gets rapped on the front pad.
Quicker, fuller, around middle. Charith Asalanka leans and defends it out.
Touch shorter, around off. Charith Asalanka blocks this one off the back foot.
Full, on middle. Blocked out.
Fuller now, outside off. Charith Asalanka defends it out.
Ravichandran Ashwin goes 'round the wicket, serves a fuller ball, around middle and leg. Pathum Nissanka leans and defends this one.
Flatter ball, shorter, around middle. Pathum Nissanka defends it off the back foot.
Loopy ball now, fuller, around middle. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out solidly.
Ravichandran Ashwin goes over the wicket, serves a shorter one, turning it in, on middle. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out off the back foot.
Slower through the air, full, around off. Pathum Nissanka defends it out solidly.
Tossed up nicely on middle. Nissanka gets forward and defends it towards the leg side.  That will be stumps on Day 2!

NO BALL! Mohammed Shami comes from 'round the wicket, serves a length ball, angling in, around middle. Charith Asalanka blocks it out off the back foot. Mohammed Shami has overstepped here and a no ball is called. Not an ideal start for Shami!
Another good-length delivery, around middle. Charith Asalanka defends it out.
Angling in, around middle and leg, on a length. Charith Asalanka taps it towards mid-wicket.
Another length delivery, around off. Charith Asalanka blocks it out solidly.
Outside off, on a length. Charith Asalanka taps it towards point and scampers through to the other end for a single.
Mohammed Shami goes over the wicket now, serves a fuller ball, sliding down leg. Pathum Nissanka misses his flick.
Good-length delivery, on middle, at 144.5 clicks. Pathum Nissanka shows the full face of his bat and blocks it out.
Ashwin begins with a loopy ball, fuller, outside off. Charith Asalanka leans and blocks it out.
Tosses it up, full in length, around middle. Charith Asalanka drives it to the fielder at short cover.
Loopy ball again, around off. Charith Asalanka presses forward and defends it out.

A tough chance goes down! Slower through the air again, full again, around middle. Charith Asalanka steps down the pitch and lifts it towards short cover. Rohit Sharma there stretches his right hand in the air, gets his hand to it but fails to grab the ball. Single taken!
Fuller again, on middle. Pathum Nissanka pushes it towards mid on.
Tosses it up, on middle. Pathum Nissanka defends it out.
FOUR! First boundary of the morning! Mohammed Shami drops it short now, on middle. Charith Asalanka pulls it towards deep square leg for a cracking boundary.
Beaten! On a length, outside off, hint of away movement there. Charith Asalanka stays in his crease and tries to block it but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Charith Asalanka blocks it out off the back foot.
Tad fuller now, outside off. Charith Asalanka presses forward and defends it out.
Spraying it down the leg side, on a length. Charith Asalanka looks to flick but misses.
Outside off, length. Charith Asalanka leaves it alone.
Flighted delivery, on middle, fuller in length. Pathum Nissanka has pushed it back to the bowler.

DROPPED! Another tough chance goes down! Tosses it up again, full, on middle. Pathum Nissanka steps down and lifts it towards mid-wicket. Shreyas Iyer runs to his right, slides to catch the ball, he gets his hands to it but drops it. He had to cover a lot of ground. Single taken!
Loopy ball, on middle. Charith Asalanka blocks it out.
Tosses it up again, around off. Charith Asalanka leans and defends it out solidly.
Loopy delivery again, fuller, around off, Charith Asalanka pushes it to cover.
Flighted delivery, on middle. Charith Asalanka defends it out.
On a length, around off. Pathum Nissanka leans and tries to defend but the ball goes off the inside edge towards the leg side.
An appeal for LBW, but turned down! Very full, coming back in, on the pads. Pathum Nissanka looks to flick but misses and gets rapped on the pads. That was definitely sliding down leg.
On a length, outside off. Pathum Nissanka defends it out.
FOUR! Edgy runs! Good-length delivery, outside off. Pathum Nissanka leans to drive but gets an outside edge towards third man for a boundary.
A stifled appeal for LBW, but not given! Length ball, nipping back in on the pads. Pathum Nissanka tries to flick but misses and gets hit on the pad. Once again sliding down leg.
Fuller now, around off. Pathum Nissanka drives to the fielder at cover.
Touch shorter, turning away, outside off. Charith Asalanka cuts it to the fielder at point.
Loopy ball, full, around off. Charith Asalanka leans and defends it out.

A beauty! What a delivery by Ravichandran Ashwin! Full again, slower through the air, turning away. Charith Asalanka leans to block this but gets beaten as the ball spins away, the ball flies just over the stump. Charith Asalanka gets lucky here!

FOUR! Streaky! Fuller again, outside off. Charith Asalanka presses forward and tries to drive, but the ball goes off the outside edge past first slip towards third man for a boundary. Sri Lanka will not mind that!
Full again, outside off. Charith Asalanka drives it past cover for a single.
Loopy ball, turning in on middle and leg. Pathum Nissanka blocks it, the ball goes just past the fielder at short leg.
Back of a length, outside off. Charith Asalanka leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery now, outside off once again. Charith Asalanka defends it out.
Another length delivery, shaping away, outside off. Charith Asalanka shoulders his arms.
Fuller now, shaping back in, around middle and leg. Charith Asalanka knocks it towards short mid-wicket.
Very full again, around middle. Charith Asalanka drills it to the fielder at mid on.
Pitches it up again, around middle, at 138.2 clicks. Charith Asalanka pushes it back to the bowler. A maiden for Shami!
FOUR! Nissanka finds a boundary this time. Slightly shorter on middle. Nissanka goes back and pulls it towards backward square leg for a boundary. Good shot!
Goes fuller and slower through the air, on off. Nissanka goes forward and blocks it out.
FOUR! Another boundary and this time good use of the wrists! Fuller delivery on off and middle. Nissanka works it left of mid on for a boundary. He is a talented player and he is showing it here now.
Slower and turning into Nissanka. He drives it back to the bowler.
Tad shorter and turning into Nissanka from middle. He goes back and works it towards the leg side.
On off and a bit quicker this time. Nissanka defends this off the back foot again.
Back of a length, around leg. Charith Asalanka works it to fine leg for a single.
Back of a length again, around off. Nissanka pushes this off the inside half of his blade past Bumrah to mid off.
FOUR! Again, the positive intent from Nissanka! A shorter delivery with a bit of width this time. Nissanka cuts it through point for a boundary.
That's much better! A good-length delivery around off and a hint of shape into the batter. Nissanka blocks it out towards the off side.
A good-length delivery around off again. Nissanka defends this off the front foot now.
A good-length delivery and a bit wider this time. Nissanka opens the face of his blade and gets it through backward point for a couple.
Quicker and slightly shorter on off. Charith Asalanka punches it to covers. Vihari does well there to stop it.
Slower in the air this time, on off at 84.9 kph. Charith Asalanka defends this off the front foot.
Loopy delivery, on off. Charith Asalanka defends this again off the front foot.
Nicely tossed up again, on off. Charith Asalanka is well forward and defends it again.
Another lovely delivery, around off. Fuller and slower in the air. Charith Asalanka blocks it out.

Ohhh....huge appeal from Ashwin but the umpire turns it down! A quicker delivery and coming through with the arm this time. Charith Asalanka thinks that it will turn away and tries to leave it. However, the ball follows it line and hits him on the back leg. However, as the umpire denies it, Indians too decide to not take a review.
FOUR! Another boundary for Nissanka! A good-length delivery, around off. Nissanka opens the face of his blade and gets it through the gully region for a boundary.
A length delivery, on off. Nissanka blocks it out.
This time Bumrah goes for a yorker on middle. Credit to Nissanka, he digs it out towards the leg side.
This time on a length and around off. Nissanka defends it off the front foot.

Slower delivery and finds the outside edge this time. This is on a good length around off. Nissanka pushes forward to defend but the ball catches the outside edge of his blade. It goes right of Pant behind the stumps and he stops it with a dive as the ball does not carry to him.
A brilliant yorker, on off to end the over. Nissanka digs it out. Superb bowling.
Nicely tossed up on off. Charith Asalanka lifts this over covers inside out and gets a couple of runs as the ball falls in the vacant region.
Tossed up delivery, on off. Charith Asalanka blocks it out.
Another loopy delivery, around off. Charith Asalanka defends this off the front foot. The ball catches the outside edge of his blade but falls short of the second slip fielder.
Flighted delivery, on off. Nissanka plays it back to the bowler.
On middle this time. Nissanka works it towards mid-wicket.
Goes fuller, on off. Nissanka drives it to mid off and takes a single. That will be fifty for Nissanka. Very good innings under pressure from the young man.
A length delivery, around off. Nissanka defends it towards the off side.
Another good-length delivery around off. Nissanka blocks it towards the off side.
A good bouncer this time on middle. Nissanka ducks under it quite comfortably.
Back of a length, on middle. Nissanka rides the bounce and blocks it out.
A good-length delivery, on off a bit slower too. Nissanka blocks this off the front foot.
Back of a length, on middle. Nissanka blocks it out off the back foot.
FOUR! Very good shot from Charith Asalanka! A fuller delivery on middle. Charith Asalanka sweeps it and sweeps it quite well for a boundary towards deep square leg fence.
Slightly shorter and turning away. Charith Asalanka gets squared up and defends it off the outside edge towards the off side.
Slower delivery on off. Charith Asalanka blocks it out.
This is quicker on off. Charith Asalanka blocks it out.
FOUR! Another lovely shot! Tossed up on middle. Charith Asalanka slog-sweeps it towards deep mid-wicket for a boundary. That brings the 50 partnership between these two!
A flatter delivery on middle and leg. Charith Asalanka works it towards fine leg for a single.
Bumrah goes 'round the wicket on length and on the off stump line. Charith Asalanka blocks it out.
On a length, on middle. Charith Asalanka blocks it out solidly yet again.
Well bowled and well played! This is very full on middle. Charith Asalanka blocks it out.
A good-length delivery, around off at 141.6 kph. Charith Asalanka defends this off the front foot.
FOUR! Charith Asalanka is finding his mojo now! Back of a length, around off. Charith Asalanka stays tall in his crease and punches it through covers for a boundary.

OUT! Charith Asalanka departs and Jasprit Bumrah breaks this partnership! What a brilliant slower delivery to get rid of the dangerous Charith Asalanka. A slower delivery, on a good length that pitches on the off stump line. Charith Asalanka looks to defend it from his crease but gets beaten by the lack of pace. The ball hits his pads and there is a huge appeal. However, the umpire is not interested. Indian players have a long discussion and Rohit Sharma takes a review at the last moment. The replays roll in and the UltraEdge shows no bat involved. The Ball Tracker rolls and it shows three reds. So the decision will be overturned and Bumrah strikes. Absolutely fantastic stuff from Bumrah!
Howout: lbw b Jasprit Bumrah

Commentary: Jadeja starts with a flatter delivery on off. Nissanka goes back and pushes it back to the bowler.
Slower in the air, this time, on off. Nissanka blocks this off the front foot.
A bit of outside edge this time. Nissanka defends this full delivery, on off. The ball catches the outside edge and goes towards backward point region for a single.
Quicker and fuller delivery on off. Niroshan Dickwella looks to sweep but the ball hits him on his gloves.
Again some turn into the batter. On off and fuller. Niroshan Dickwella defends this off the inside half of his blade to backward square leg for a single.
Flatter trajectory, on off. Nissanka defends it solidly off the front foot. This one goes through with the arm
A teriffic yorker on off. Niroshan Dickwella digs it out. What a bowlers this man is!
Another yorker on middle. Niroshan Dickwella digs it out again. A bit slower this time.
A fuller delivery on middle and leg. Niroshan Dickwella works it towards short mid-wicket.
This time a pacy good-length delivery on off at 147 kph. Niroshan Dickwella gets the inside edge of his blade as he looks to defend it. The ball goes towards the fine leg region for a single.
This time, on a length, around middle at 143.7 kph. Nissanka blocks it out.
An attempted yorker turns into a full toss on middle. Nissanka defends it towards short mid-wicket.
Quicker, turning it in on middle. Niroshan Dickwella gets down to sweep but misses. A stifled appeal there for LBW, but turned down.
Fuller ball, outside off. Niroshan Dickwella looks to defend but does so with the inner half of his bat.
Loopy ball, around off. Niroshan Dickwella blocks it out.

OUT! CAUGHT! Ravindra Jadeja strikes this time! India have got another wicket. Niroshan Dickwella goes back early. A fuller ball, turning it in around middle. Niroshan Dickwella looks to sweep this towards deep mid-wicket, but he gets a top edge of his bat. The ball flies high and goes towards the deep mid-wicket region. Shreyas Iyer is placed perfectly there he runs forward and takes a sharp in the end. Sri Lanka have lost their sixth!
Howout: c Shreyas Iyer b Ravindra Jadeja

Commentary: An appeal for LBW, but turned down! A fuller ball, turning away, around the leg pole. Suranga Lakmal leans to defend but misses and gets rapped on the pad. India opt for a review! No bat involved confirms UltraEdge. Ball Tracker shows it was pitching outside leg. The on-field decision stands. India lose a review!

OUT! TAKEN! Another one bites the dust and this is poor shot-selection from such an experienced player! A tossed up delivery, on middle. Suranga Lakmal dances down the track strangely and looks to heave it towards the leg side. He completely miscues it and the ball goes in the air towards the mid off region as the ball slices off the outside edge of his blade. Ravichandran Ashwin settles under it and takes a good catch. This is disaster for Sri Lanka, they were looking so good in the first hour of the play but are falling apart now.
Howout: c Ravichandran Ashwin b Ravindra Jadeja

Commentary: Shorter one, around off. Pathum Nissanka defends it out.
Fuller, outside off. Pathum Nissanka pushes it towards third man and denies a single.
Slower through the air now, full, around middle. Pathum Nissanka defends it out.
Very full again, on middle. Pathum Nissanka pushes it past mid-wicket for a single.
Touch shorter, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it on the off side.
Another fuller ball, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya leans to defend but does so with the inner half of his bat.
Quicker and fuller, around middle. Pathum Nissanka presses forward and blocks it out.
Flatter, on middle and full in length. Pathum Nissanka steps down and pushes it towards mid off.
FOUR! Fuller ball, on middle. Pathum Nissanka gets low and sweeps it with inner half of his bat towards deep square leg for a boundary.
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries! Full again, on middle. Pathum Nissanka gets down on his knee and swipes this uppishly towards deep square leg for another boundary.
Loopy ball, full and around off. Pathum Nissanka defends it out.
Tosses it up, full in length, around off. Pathum Nissanka leans and blocks it out.
Good-length delivery, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it off the front foot.
Tad fuller, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya leans to defend but the ball goes off the outside towards second slip, who collects it on the bounce.

OUT! TAKEN! Another one bites the dust! India are all over Sri Lanka! Mohammed Shami comes into the attack and strikes! Shami drops it short now, around middle. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to back away and ducks, but leaves his bat hanging. The ball goes off the top of the bat and lobs behind the short leg fielder. Mayank Agarwal has plenty of time to go back and take an easy catch. Sri Lanka are now 8 down!
Howout: c Mayank Agarwal b Mohammed Shami

Commentary: Fuller now, around off. Vishwa Fernando blocks it out.
On a length, outside off. Vishwa Fernando leaves it alone.
Shorter ball, around middle. Vishwa Fernando ducks under it.
Fuller in length, around off. Pathum Nissanka steps down and pushes it to cover.
Shorter ball, around off. Pathum Nissanka defends it towards mid off.
Back of a length, around middle. Pathum Nissanka pushes it towards mid on for a single.
Loopy ball, around middle. Vishwa Fernando blocks it out.

OUT! EDGED AND TAKEN! Ravindra Jadeja is now one away from his five-wicket haul. A loopy ball, turning away a tad around middle. Vishwa Fernando leans to defend this, but the ball goes off the outside edge towards Rohit Sharma at second slip who pouches it safely. Wickets continue to tumble and Sri Lanka are now 9 down!
Howout: c Rohit Sharma b Ravindra Jadeja

Commentary: OUT! CLEANED HIM UP! Ravindra Jadeja gets his five-wicket haul! What a Test match he is having! Ravindra Jadeja keeps it simple, tad quicker, attacking the stumps. Lahiru Kumara looks to defend this without any foot movement, and the ball goes past his outside edge and knocks the off stump. Ravindra Jadeja will be on a hat-trick in the next innings! Sri Lanka are bundled out for 174! India have a lead of 400.
Howout: b Ravindra Jadeja

Commentary: A loopy ball, full and on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne leans and defends it out.
Slower through the air again, on middle, full again. Lahiru Thirimanne presses forward and blocks it out.
Full again, on middle. Lahiru Thirimanne defends it out.
Tosses it up, on middle. Lahiru Kumara blocks it out soldily.
Fuller, around off. Lahiru Thirimanne pushes it towards cover.
Beaten! Tosses it up, outside off, spinning away. Lahiru Thirimanne presses forward to defend but gets beaten.

NO BALL AND FOUR! On a length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne lunges to defend but the ball goes off the outside edge past  gully for a boundary. Mohammed Shami has overstepped here and a no ball is called.
Fuller now, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it towards mid-wicket.
Full again, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it back to the bowler.
Beaten! On a length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to defend but misses.
Another length delivery, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it off the back foot.
Fuller now, around middle and leg. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to flick but the ball goes off the inner half of the bat towards square leg.
FOUR! Edgy runs! Length ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne tries to push this, but the ball goes off the outside edge towards third man for a boundary.
Loopy ball, outside off. Lahiru Thirimanne leans and blocks it out.
Slower through the air, full, around off. Lahiru Thirimanne leans and defends it from teh outer half of his bat.

OUT! EDGED AND TAKEN! Ravichandran Ashwin strikes and grabs the first wicket! He gets a left-hander once again! An early breakthrough for India! A loopy ball, very full, this one lands around middle and turns away a tad. Lahiru Thirimanne presses forward and looks to block this, but the ball goes off the outside edge towards Rohit Sharma at second slip, who dives to his right and takes a sharp catch. Lahiru Thirimanne walks back early!
Howout: c Rohit Sharma b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: Tossed up around middle. Nissanka looks to defend it but the ball turns into him with some extra boucne and hits him on the body.
Another loopy delivery, around off. Nissanka looks to defend but gets beaten off the outside edge.
A flatter delivery on middle. Nissanka works it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Tad shorter, around middle. Pathum Nissanka looks to defend but misses and gets hit on the pads. No hat-trick for Ravindra Jadeja!
Quicker, shorter again, around off. Pathum Nissanka blocks it out.
Very full on this occasion, on middle. Pathum Nissanka pushes it towards mid on.
Fuller in length again, on middle. Pathum Nissanka lunges and blocks it out.
Tossed up nicely on middle. Nissanka gets forward and blocks it.
Fuller delivery on off. Nissanka drives it to covers.
A flatter delivery at 89.5 kph, on off to start. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it to covers.
Slower in the air this time. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out towards the off side.
This time beaten! Nicely tossed up around off and turning away. Dimuth Karunaratne presses forward to defend but the ball beats the outside edge of his blade.
Goes fuller on off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it to covers. The fielder there misfields and a single is taken.
A slightly shorter delivery down the leg side and turning further into Nissanka. He lets it go.
Turns into Nissanka again, this time from middle. Nissanka tries to work it towards the leg side. Misses and the ball hits his pads and goes behind square on the leg side for a single.
A fuller delivery, on off. Nissanka drives it to covers.
Tossed up nicely this time, on off. Nissanka gets forward and blocks it out.
Tossed up around off. Nissanka skips down the track and pushes it towards the off side for a single.
Fuller on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne works it through mid-wicket for a couple.
Loopy delivery around off. Dimuth Karunaratne takes a good stride forward and defends it towards the off side.
Flighted delivery on off. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it off the front foot.
FOUR! Good shot by Nissanka! A fuller delivery on off. Nissanka sweeps it to deep square leg for a boundary.
Tossed up, outside off. Nissanka presses forward to defend it but the ball beats the outside edge of his blade.
Slower through the air, on off. Nissanka gets forward and looks to defend but the ball turns into him and hits him on his body.
Turn again, this is pitched on off and turning into Nissanka. He defends it off the back foot.

OUT! TAKEN! A big wicket for India, the only player who showed some resilience in the first innings walks back cheaply this time. This is a superb set up by Ashwin. After some slower deliveries, he pushes this one quicker around off. Nissanka gets forward to block it but the ball catches the outside edge and Pant takes a good catch behind the stumps. There is an appeal but the umpire says no. India take a review and the UltraEdge confirms an edge and Nissanka has to walk back. Ravichandran Ashwin strikes once again and Sri Lanka lose their second wicket.
Howout: c Rishabh Pant b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: Tossed up nicely again, on off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
A flatter delivery on off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it towards the off side.
FOUR! Boundary for the skipper. Confident shot! Tossed up, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it through covers for a lovely boundary.
On middle at 90.5 kph. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it solidly off the front foot.
Again quicker through the air on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne lunges forward and blocks it.
Fullish delivery on off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it solidly yet again.
This time a bit shorter and flatter again, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne goes back and pushes it towards the off side.
Quicker delivery on middle. Angelo Mathews works it towards the leg side.
Slower through the air, on off. Angelo Mathews skips down the track and pushes it to long on for a single.
Tossed up nicely on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks this off the front foot.
Loopy delivery on off again. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it to covers this time.
Nicely bowled on middle and fuller. With a drift on it. Dimuth Karunaratne defends this off the front foot.

FOUR! Ohh...nearly knocked him over! A flatter and quicker delivery angling into middle. Dimuth Karunaratne goes back to play it but is cramped for room and gets the inside edge past stumps. The ball races towards the long leg fence for a boundary.
A fuller delivery on off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Dropped this time! Yadav pitches this on off. Angelo Mathews presses forward to defend but the ball catches the outside edge of his blade and goes towards Kohli at first slip. He, however, drops it.
On middle this time. Angelo Mathews works it behind square on the leg side this time.
FOUR! This will ease from nerves! A flatter delivery and drifting on middle and leg. Angelo Mathews works it fine towards the long leg fence for a boundary.
Fullish delivery on middle. Angelo Mathews works it towards mid-wicket and takes a single. A bit of mix-up between the batters but a comfortable single in the end.
A slightly shorter delivery and outside off. It turns away and beats Dimuth Karunaratne as he looks to cut it.
Tosses it up, very full, on middle. Angelo Mathews eases it down to long for a single.
Full again, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it towards cover.
Slower through the air, full, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne leans and blocks it out.
Shorter now, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne taps it towards mid-wicket.
Beaten! Slightly quicker through the air, full, turning away, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leans to defend but misses as the ball spins away from him.
Loopy ball, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne lunges and blocks it out.
Fuller ball, around middle, slower through the air. Angelo Mathews pushes it back to the bowler.
Shorter now, turning it in, on middle. Angelo Mathews hangs back and pushes it towards square leg.
Tosses it up, on middle. Angelo Mathews steps down and knocks it towards long on for a single.
Jayant Yadav goes 'round the wicket now, serves a fuller ball, loopy delivery, around off, Dimuth Karunaratne presses forward to block it.
Flighted deliver, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leans and drives it to the fielder at short cover.
Outside off, full in length. Dimuth Karunaratne leaves it alone.
Shorter ball, coming in on middle. Angelo Mathews stays back and pushes it back to the bowler.
Slower now, full, on middle. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Slow once again, full in length, around off. Angelo Mathews steps down and eases it to long on for a single.
Turning away, full, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it to cover.
Fuller now, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it to mid off.
FOUR! Nicely done! Slightly shorter now, spinning away from outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne stays back and slashes it past cover for a boundary.
Tossed up delivery, around middle. Angelo Mathews steps down the pitch and knocks it towards mid on for a quick single.
Fuller ball, loopy again, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out.
Slightly shorter, outside off, turning away. Dimuth Karunaratne chops it towards point.
Much fuller now, slower through thd air, around off. Dimuth Karunaratne leans and defends it out solidly.
Full again, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne lunges and pushes it towards short cover.
Flighted delivery, full, around off. Blocked out.
Slower through the air, on middle, full in length. Angelo Mathews defends it out.
Floated delivery, very full again, on middle. Angelo Mathews presses forward and blocks it out.
Turning it in on middle, fuller ball. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards leg slip, who collects it on a bounce.
Outside off, loopy ball. Angelo Mathews defends it out.
Fuller again, spinning it in around middle. Angelo Mathews taps it towards mid-wicket.
Loopy ball, full, on middle. Angelo Mathews knocks it back to the bowler. A maiden for Ravichandran Ashwin!
Swing and a miss! Fuller ball, wide of off, at 133.5 clicks. Dimuth Karunaratne leans to drive but misses.
Pitches it up again, angling in on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne works it towards the fielder at mid-wicket.
Full again, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne tries to push this away, but the goes off the outside edge towards backward point.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Mohammed Shami drops it short now, on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne gets on top on the bounce and pulls it towards deep square leg for a boundary.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Mohammed Shami comes into the attack and strikes! What a follow-up delivery by him. A peach of a delivery! This one lands on a length, hint of away movement there, around the fourth stump line. Dimuth Karunaratne tries to defend, but the ball goes off the outside edge towards the keeper. Rishabh Pant dives to his left and takes a good low catch. A big wicket for India. Sri Lanka lose their third wicket.
Howout: c Rishabh Pant b Mohammed Shami

Commentary: Fuller, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it past cover for a single. He gets off the mark on his very first delivery!
Loopy ball, on middle. Dhananjaya de Silva defends it out.
Fuller again, around middle, slower through the air. Dhananjaya de Silva leans and clips it away from the short leg fielder.
Fuller again, around middle. Dhananjaya de Silva works it away towards square leg for a single.
FOUR! Top shot! Very full again, outside off. Angelo Mathews drills it past mid off for a cracking boundary.
Tosses it up, very full again, on middle. Angelo Mathews knocks it towards the mid-wicket fielder who fails to stop the ball. Two taken!
Tad shorter, on middle. Angelo Mathews clips it to the fielder at square leg.
Pitches it up, down the leg side. Dhananjaya de Silva misses his flick.
FOUR! Excellent shot! Perfectly timed shot. Another overpitched delivery, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva leans forward and drives it past cover for a boundary.
Full again, around off. Dhananjaya de Silva drives again but finds the fielder at mid off.
Shorter ball now, on middle, at 138.5. Dhananjaya de Silva hops and defends it out.
Back of a length, angling in on middle. Dhananjaya de Silva clips it over mid-wicket for a brace.
On a length, shaping away, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva leaves it alone.
Loopy ball, very full, on middle. Angelo Mathews steps down and pushes it to the right of the bowler. Jayant Yadav dives to his right and makes a good stop.
Tosses it up again, fuller ball, on middle. Angelo Mathews works it away to the fielder at mid-wicket.
Slower through the air, on middle, full in length. Angelo Mathews dances down the track and whips it towards deep square leg for a single.
Shorter ball now, spinning it in on middle. Dhananjaya de Silva stays back and taps it towards the fielder at short leg.
Back of a length, around middle, turning it in. Dhananjaya de Silva rocks back and pushes it away from the short leg fielder.
Quicker again, on middle. Dhananjaya de Silva clips it past square leg for a single.
Fuller ball, spraying it down the leg side. Dhananjaya de Silva looks to flick but misses.
On a length again, down the leg side. Dhananjaya de Silva looks to tuck it away once again but fails to get any bat on it.
Back of a length, around off. Dhananjaya de Silva stands tall and tries to push this away, but he manages to get an inside edge towards mid-wicket.

FOUR LEG BYES! Angling in, on the pads, on a length. Dhananjaya de Silva misses his flick, but the ball brushes off his pads and beats the diving keeper. The ball races away towards fine leg for a boundary.
Shaping away a tad, outside off, fraction shorter this time. Dhananjaya de Silva taps it towards point.

An appeal for LBW, but tuned down! Length ball, nipping back in on the pads. Dhananjaya de Silva misses his flick and gets pinged on the pads. That was probably sliding down leg. Good decision not to take the review!
Quicker and fuller on off. Angelo Mathews defends it towards short leg.
Another delivery on the off stump line. Angelo Mathews gets well forward and blocks it.
This time a bit shorter on middle. Angelo Mathews goes back and works it towards short leg.
Goes a tad fuller and quciker on off. Angelo Mathews works it towards silly mid-wicket.
Tossed up this time on off. Angelo Mathews takes a good stride forward and blocks it.
He sticks to that off stump line and serves this fuller. Angelo Mathews blocks it off the front foot soldily.

FOUR! Boundary and Dhananjaya de Silva has started well with couple of boundaries! A full delivery on middle and leg. Dhananjaya de Silva flicks it through square leg region for a boundary. Nice shot.
A good-length delivery, on off. Dhananjaya de Silva blocks it out.
A good-length delivery, around off. Dhananjaya de Silva drives it off the inside half of his blade back to Shami.
Goes fuller on middle and hint of reverse swing there into the batter. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it to mid on.
A good-length delivery, outside off and shaping away this time. Dhananjaya de Silva leaves it alone.
Goes fuller again, on middle at 140.9 kph. Dhananjaya de Silva drives it back to the bowler.
Slightly shorter and turning into middle and leg. Angelo Mathews works it behind square on the leg side.
Tossed up nicely, outside off. Angelo Mathews blocks this off the front foot.
Bit slower this time and pulls his length back slightly on off. Angelo Mathews works it towards the leg side.
Shorter and outside off. Angelo Mathews punches it to covers.
Short and wide outside off. Angelo Mathews looks to cut but the ball turns and bounces to beat the outside edge of his blade.
Quicker and fuller on off. Angelo Mathews gets good stride forward and defends it.
Back of a length, on middle and angling into the batter. Dhananjaya de Silva blocks it out towards the off side.
A good-length delivery around off and nipping into the batter. Dhananjaya de Silva looks to cut but gets the inside edge past stumps.
On a length, on off. Dhananjaya de Silva blocks it soldily this time.
Hits the length hard again, on off. Dhananjaya de Silva gets back and blocks it out.
Short ball this time on off. Dhananjaya de Silva sways away from the line of the ball. Expect a fuller ball any time soon.
FOUR! Yes, he goes fuller but Dhananjaya de Silva is upto the task! This is overpitched on off. Dhananjaya de Silva leans forward and drives it past mid off for a boundary.
ohh...Jadeja starts off with a beauty! Slower through the air, on off. Angelo Mathews pushes forward to defend but the ball turns away and beats the outside edge of his blade.
A fuller delivery on off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Goes fuller on middle this time. Angelo Mathews plays it back to the bowler.
Tossed up on off this time. Angelo Mathews defends it solidly.
This is fuller and around off. Angelo Mathews drives it to deepish mid off for a single.
Flighted delivery on off. Dhananjaya de Silva gets well forward and blocks it.
Lovely delivery! A good-length delivery, around off. Angelo Mathews looks to defend it but the ball seams away and beats the outside edge of his blade.
A fuller delivery, on off. Angelo Mathews drives it to mid on.

Ohh...too good to get the outside edge! This is on a good length and around off. Angelo Mathews looks to defend it and plays for the one that comes into him. However, the ball seams away and completely squares him up.
A brilliant inswinging yorker on middle and leg this time. Angelo Mathews digs it out.
A slower delivery, on off. Angelo Mathews is aware of it and blocks it out.
On middle and leg. A length ball this time. Angelo Mathews works it past square leg and gets a couple.
Fuller and quicker on off. Dhananjaya de Silva blocks this off the front foot.
This time slower in the air, on off. Dhananjaya de Silva steps out and doesn't reach the pitch of the ball and defends it.
Another loopy delivery on off. Dhananjaya de Silva skips down the track and defends it off the front foot. A stifled appeal as the ball is close to the pads but no damage done.
FOUR! Slightly shorter this time and Dhananjaya de Silva takes full advantage of it. He goes back and uses his wrists to work it towards the mid-wicket region for a boundary.
A fuller delivery on off. Dhananjaya de Silva blocks it out.
Tossed up around off. Dhananjaya de Silva defends this solidly yet again.
Bumrah starts with a short delivery on middle. Angelo Mathews ducks under it.
Back of a length, on off. Angelo Mathews defends it solidly off the back foot.

FOUR BYES! Ohh this one beats everyone! An attempted yorker down the leg side. Angelo Mathews looks to flick it but misses. Pant dives to his left to stop it. However, the ball hits his gloves and goes towards the fence.
Back of a length, on off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
A full delivery on off. Angelo Mathews drives it to the short cover fielder.
On a length, on middle. Angelo Mathews defends it towards the leg side.
A flatter and quicker delivery on off. Dhananjaya de Silva goes back and blocks it.
Slower in the air, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva leaves it alone.
On middle this time. Dhananjaya de Silva is comfortable in the front foot defence.
Tossed up on off. Dhananjaya de Silva blocks this off the front foot.
Tossed up on off. Dhananjaya de Silva drives it to deepish mid off for a single.
Slower in the air, on off. Angelo Mathews blocks this off the front foot.
On a good length, around off and slower in pace at 122.7 kph. Dhananjaya de Silva gets forward and blocks it out.
On a length, on middle. Dhananjaya de Silva works it towards short mid-wicket.
A full delivery around leg at 142.8 kph. Dhananjaya de Silva flicks it to fine leg for a single.
A slower delivery, outside off at 129.1 kph. Angelo Mathews defends it towards the off side.
A short delivery on off. Angelo Mathews sways away from the line of the ball.
On a length, on off. Angelo Mathews defends it towards the leg side.
Fuller ball, quicker, on middle. Dhananjaya de Silva defends it out.
Slower now, full again, on middle. Dhananjaya de Silva lunges and blocks it out.
Tosses it up, on middle. Dhananjaya de Silva blocks it out.
Touch shorter, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva hangs back and dabs it towards point.
Loopy ball, full, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva defends it out.

EDGED AND FOUR! Dhananjaya de Silva gets lucky there! A fuller ball, spinning away, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva leans to drive but the ball goes off the outside edge and flies between the fielder at first slip and short gully. The ball races away towards the third man fence for a boundary..
Turning it in on middle, shorter ball. Angelo Mathews stays back and taps it towards square leg.
Shorter, spinning in, outside off. Angelo Mathews hangs back and pushes it towards cover.
Outside off, back of a length. Angelo Mathews dabs it towards backward point.
Spinning it in again, aroun middle. Angelo Mathews knocks it towards long on for a single.
Much fuller now, slower through the air, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva leans and pushes it towards cover for a single.
Pulls his length back now, outside off. Angelo Mathews stays back and taps it to point.
Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva taps it towards cover.
Fuller now, around middle. Dhananjaya de Silva flicks it past mid-wicket for a brace. There was an easy third run there, but Angelo Mathews denies it!
Shorter again, around off. Dhananjaya de Silva blocks it out off the back foot.
Quicker now, outside off, tad shorter. Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it towards extra cover!

OUT! CAUGHT! Ravindra Jadeja displays his magic and breaks this partnership! He grabs his first wicket of the innings and India have got their fourth wicket! A soft dismissal this one! Ravindra Jadeja tosses this one up, fuller, around middle, turns away as well. Dhananjaya de Silva leans and tries to go inside-out, ends up just chipping it as the ball goes off the top of the bat towards extra-cover. Shreyas Iyer times his jump perfectly and pouches the ball safely.
Howout: c Shreyas Iyer b Ravindra Jadeja

Commentary: Tossed up delivery on off at 83.5 kph. Charith Asalanka plays it back to Jadeja.
Nicely tossed up around off. Angelo Mathews skips down the track and hits it back to Ashwin.
Slower in the air, outside off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
SIX! Probabaly the last over before Tea and Angelo Mathews decides to take Ashwin on. A tossed up delivery on off. Angelo Mathews skips down the track and tonks it over long on for a biggie.
A flatter delivery on off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
A shorter delivery and turning into middle. Angelo Mathews works it towards the leg side.
Goes fuller on middle. Angelo Mathews takes a big stride forward and works it towards mid-wicket.
SIX! Ohh...a biggie to get off the mark! A fuller delivery on off. Charith Asalanka skips down the track and hammers it over deep mid-wicket for a biggie.
SIX! He goes after Jadeja again and gets full points again. A fuller delivery on off. Charith Asalanka dances down the track and slams it  straight down the ground for a maximum.
Slighlty shorter around off and turning into Charith Asalanka. He blocks it out.
Loopy delivery, outside off. Charith Asalanka skips down the track and mistimes his heave towards mid-wicket. Strange batting this!

FOUR! He goes for it again and gets a boundary again! The field was brought in and Charith Asalanka takes up the challenge. A quicker delivery on middle. Charith Asalanka sweeps it over the square leg fielder for a boundary.

FOUR! He finishes the session with another boundary! This time a better shot! Quicker and flatter around off. Charith Asalanka waits for it and guides it towards the third man region for a boundary. Sri Lanka are 120/4 in their second innings at Tea on Day 3.
Fuller ball, spinning it in on middle. Angelo Mathews taps it past mid-wicket for a single.
Loopy ball, fuller, on middle. Charith Asalanka leans and defends it out.

OUT! CAUGHT! Ravichandran Ashwin strikes for the third time now! He now goes past Kapil Dev, and becomes the second-highest wicket-taker for India in Test cricket! That was his 435th Test wicket. Take a bow, Ravichandran Ashwin! Another lefty goes back to the hut because of Ravichandran Ashwin! A loopy ball, fuller, spinning away.
