Charith Asalanka leans to defend, but the ball goes off his glove, onto the pads of Pant and then lobs up towards Virat Kohli at first slip. Kohli sticks out his left hand, but the ball does not stick. It lobs up in the air and then misses his palms again. But the former Indian skipper is alert and manages to catch it near his abdomen. Sri Lanka have lost half their side now!
Howout: c Virat Kohli b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: Tossed up delivery, on off. Niroshan Dickwella blocks it out.
On middle this time and a bit quicker. Niroshan Dickwella gets forward and defends it.
Pushed wider outside off. Niroshan Dickwella drives it to covers.
Quicker, on middle. Angelo Mathews defends it out.

OUT! LBW! Another one goes down! Sri Lanka are in all sorts of trouble here! Ravindra Jadeja sends back Angelo Mathews now. Touch shorter, this one lands around middle and turns away towards off. Angelo Mathews stays back and tries to flick this on the leg side, but he misses as the ball turns away from him and gets hit on his back pad. An appeal for LBW, and the umpire raises his finger. Angelo Mathews decides to go for the review anyway. No bat involved and Ball Tracker shows three reds. That's the end of Angelo Mathews!
Howout: lbw b Ravindra Jadeja

Commentary: Nicely tossed up on off. Suranga Lakmal presses foward to defend but the ball catches the outside edge of his blade and goes toward short gully.
A quicker delivery on off. Suranga Lakmal blocks it out.

OUT! Double strike for Ravindra Jadeja! Sri Lanka are throwing away their wickets here. Ravindra Jadeja grabs this third and Sri Lanka are now 7 down! Another fuller ball, around middle. Suranga Lakmal steps down the pitch and tries to heave this over mid-on, but he does so with the inner half of his bat and the ball goes straight to Jayant Yadav at mid-on who makes no mistake! What an over this is turning out to be from Ravindra Jadeja!
Howout: c Jayant Yadav b Ravindra Jadeja

Commentary: A flatter delivery on middle and leg. Lasith Embuldeniya works it towards the leg side.
FOUR! Fuller ball, down the leg side. Niroshan Dickwella sweeps it towards fine leg for a boundary.
Loopy ball, around off. Niroshan Dickwella leans and defends it out.
Beaten! A loopy ball again, spinning away, outside off. Niroshan Dickwella lunges to defend this but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Slower through the air, full, on middle. Niroshan Dickwella sweeps it towards fine leg for a single.
Loopy ball, this one comes in with the arm, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it out.
Fuller, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it out.
Fuller, spinning away outside off. Niroshan Dickwella looks to sweep this but misses.
Slower through the air, fuller ball, outside off. Niroshan Dickwella defends it out.
Loopy ball, outside off, spinning away. Niroshan Dickwella taps it towards silly point.
Another tossed up delivery, outside off. Niroshan Dickwella has blocked this one.
FOUR! Top shot! Fuller ball, slower through the air, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella gets down on his knee and sweeps it over mid-wicket for a boundary.
Outside off, left alone.
Loopy ball, on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it out.
Fuller now, spinning away, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to defend but gets beaten.
Slower through the air, on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it out.
Another loopy ball, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya taps it towards point.
Shorter now, arund middle. Lasith Embuldeniya pushes it back to the bowler.
Another shorter ball, around middle. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it back to the bowler.
Tossed up on off. Niroshan Dickwella blocks it out.
A flatter delivery, on off. Niroshan Dickwella pushes it to silly point.
This time beaten! A flatter delivery, around off and turning away. Niroshan Dickwella looks to defend it but the ball beats the outside edge of his blade.
Tossed up again, on off. Niroshan Dickwella blocks it out.
Loppy delivery on middle. Niroshan Dickwella defends this off the front foot.
A fuller delivery on off.  Niroshan Dickwella drives it to mid off.
Fuller ball, on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya leans and defends it out.
Turning it in, on middle, loopy ball. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it out off the front foot.
Another tossed up ball, around middle and leg. Lasith Embuldeniya leans and blocks it out.
Outside off, loopy delivery. Lasith Embuldeniya taps it towards point.
Fuller now, slower through the air. Lasith Embuldeniya pushes it towards cover.
Much quicker now, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya stays back and blocks it out.
Fuller now, on middle. Niroshan Dickwella gets forward and pushes towards cover.
Shorter now, outside off. Niroshan Dickwella stays back and cuts it towards point for a single.
Flatter adn shorter, around middle. Lasith Embuldeniya pushes it to cover.
Around middle and leg, fuller ball, slower now. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it out.
A flatter delivery on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it out.
Tossed up around off. Lasith Embuldeniya gets forward and defends it watchfully.
Tossed up around off. Niroshan Dickwella blocks this off the front foot.
Flatter and quicker on middle. Niroshan Dickwella defends this nicely under his eyes now.
Tossed up on off. Niroshan Dickwella gets well forward and blocks it.
This is down the leg side and quciker. Niroshan Dickwella looks to sweep but misses.
Loppy delivery on middle. Niroshan Dickwella gets good stride forward and blocks it.
FOUR! Nice shot by Niroshan Dickwella! A fuller delivery on middle. Niroshan Dickwella sweeps it to deep mid-wicket for a boundary.
Goes slower in the air, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks this off the front foot.
Pushed quicker on off. Lasith Embuldeniya drives it to covers for a single.
On middle and leg and turning into Niroshan Dickwella. He skips down the track and works it towards backward square leg for a single.
This is pushed quicker on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya is solid in his defence.
Another flater delivery on off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it out.
Jadeja pushes this quciker around off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it towards the off side.
Shorter ball, turning away, outside off. Niroshan Dickwella stays back and taps it to point.
Fuller now, on middle. Niroshan Dickwella gets down one his knee sweeps it towards deep square leg for a single.
Slower through the air, on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya presses forward and defends it out.
Fuller ball, spins away, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya leans to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Quicker now, drifting it in, around middle. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to defend but gets an inside edge towards square leg for a single.
Much fuller now and slower, on middle, full in length. Niroshan Dickwella blocks it out.
Outside off, fuller ball. Lasith Embuldeniya taps it towards point.
Fuller ball, turning it in on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya leans to defend but gets an inside edge onto his pads.
Another fuller ball, around off, turning it in. Lasith Embuldeniya lunges to block this but the ball goes off the inside edge towards fine leg.
Tad fuller, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya pushes it towards cover.
In the air.. but safe! A fuller ball, around middle. Lasith Embuldeniya goes for the slog-sweep but he miscues his shot towards mid on who collects it on the bounce!
Quicker now, coming back in, on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya hangs back and tries to defend but the ball goes off the outside edge away from point.
A flatter delivery and slightly shorter in length, on off. Niroshan Dickwella blocks it out.
Loopy delivery, around off. Niroshan Dickwella looks to sweep but the ball turns and bounces and takes Paant by surprise as he manages to stop it awkwardly.
Tossed up nicely on off. Niroshan Dickwella blocks it out.
On middle and quicker this time. Niroshan Dickwella works it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Flighted delivery this time, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya gets well forward and defends it.
Another loopy delivery, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya is solid on his front foot defence.
A flatter delivery turning into middle and leg. Niroshan Dickwella looks to defend it but the ball hits his pads and goes towards the leg side.
Tossed up around off. Niroshan Dickwella blocks it out.
Loopy delivery on off. Niroshan Dickwella works it towards the leg side as he skips down the track.
Goes slightly quicker this time, on off. Niroshan Dickwella gets forward to block it.
A fullish delivery on middle. Niroshan Dickwella pushes it to long on for a single.
Slower in the air, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it towards the off side.
FOUR! Nicely played, good timing this time! A length delivery angling into off from 'round the wicket. Niroshan Dickwella leans forward and drives it crisply through covers for a boundary.
On a length and down the leg side this time. Niroshan Dickwella looks to clip it away but misses. It goes back to Pant behind the stumps.

FOUR! These boundaries will give much-needed confidence to Niroshan Dickwella! A good-length delivery and a bit wide this time. Niroshan Dickwella opens the face of his blade and guides it through the gully region for a boundary.
FOUR! Third boundary and this is a poor delivery by Shami. On the pads and Niroshan Dickwella just tucks it fine towards the long leg fence for a boundary.
On a length and angling into middle this time. Niroshan Dickwella works it towards mid-wicket.
Back of a length, around off. Niroshan Dickwella punches it to covers off the back foot.
Slower in the air at 81.3 kph, on off. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks this off the front foot.
Goes 'round the wicket on off. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it quite well.
Goes slightly shorter on off. Lasith Embuldeniya goes back this time and blocks it out.
On middle and leg. Lasith Embuldeniya works it towards the leg side.
This is down the leg side and flatter. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to clip it but misses.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! The angle from 'round the wicket does the trick here and the resistance from Lasith Embuldeniya comes to an end. This is flatter and quicker around off. Lasith Embuldeniya is stuck on his crease to this fuller ball as he tries to block this one, but the ball catches the outside edge of his blade. The ball goes back to Pant and he takes a fine catch. Ravindra Jadeja grabs his fourth wicket of the innings and ninth wicket of this match! So Just two wickets away India now from wrapping this Test match on Day 3!
Howout: c Rishabh Pant b Ravindra Jadeja

Commentary: Back of a length, around off. Niroshan Dickwella steers it towards the third man region for a couple.
A length delivery, on off. Niroshan Dickwella pushes it to mid off for a single.
On a length, on off. Vishwa Fernando blocks it towards the off side.
Back of a length, on off. Vishwa Fernando blocks it out.
Goes fuller on off. Vishwa Fernando keeps it out.
Shami goes for a short delivery now around leg. Vishwa Fernando ducks under it.

NOT OUT! A beauty by Ravindra Jadeja! Tad fuller, spinning in sharply. Niroshan Dickwella stays in his crease and tries to cut this away, but the ball brushes off his pad and goes towards Pant. A huge appeal for caught behind! The umpire says no! India opts for a review! The replay rolls in and UltraEdge shows no bat involved there! Ball Tracker shows that the impact is outside the line. Niroshan Dickwella survies!
FOU! Top shot! Fuller ball, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella steps down and heaves it towards deep mid-wicket for a boundary.
Fuller ball, on middle. Niroshan Dickwella defends it out.
Fuller again, quicker one around middle. Niroshan Dickwella steps down the pitch and pushes it towards mid-wicket.
Shorter now, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella taps it to mid-wicket again.
Fuller now, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella sweeps this towards short fine for a quick single.

An appeal for LBW, but not given! A length ball, nipping back in, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella tries to push this away, but he gets a slight inside edge on to his pads. Shami thinks he has got his man and Rohit Sharma opts for a review! The replay rolls in and UltraEdge confirms the same, there was bat involved in that! India lose another review!
On a length outside off. Niroshan Dickwella taps it towards point.
FOUR! Easy pickings! Tad fuller, darting it on the pads. Niroshan Dickwella flicks it towards deep square leg for a boundary.
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries! Fuller again, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella presents the full face of the bat and drives it past mid on for a boundary.
Full again, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella taps it past mid off for a single.

OUT! LBW! Mohammed Shami strikes now! India are just one wicket away now! A length ball, nipping back in on middle. Vishwa Fernando stays in his crease and tries to flick this but he misses and gets rapped on the pads. An appeal for LBW, and the umpire raises his finger immediately. Vishwa Fernando opts for a review! No bat involved there and the Ball Tracker shows three reds! Vishwa Fernando has to walk back.
Howout: lbw b Mohammed Shami

Commentary: Fuller ball, on middle. Niroshan Dickwella reverse-sweeps this towards cover.
Fuller again, quicker now on middle. Niroshan Dickwella pushes it towards mid-wicket.
Another fuller ball, arud middle. Niroshan Dickwella tries to reverse-sweep this one, but misses this time.
Fuller, around off. Niroshan Dickwella comes forward and defends it out.
Quick, full again, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella steps down and eases it to long on for a single.
Loopy ball, around off. Lahiru Kumara leans and defends it out.
Slower through the air, outside off, fuller ball. Niroshan Dickwella pushes it towards cover.
Loopy again, around off. Niroshan Dickwella drives it towards long off.
Full again, around middle and leg. Niroshan Dickwella looks to sweep this but misses and gets hit on the pads. There is an appeal for LBW, but the umpire is unmoved!
Outside off, shorter now. Niroshan Dickwella taps it towards point.

Fuller in length, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella steps down and knocks it down to mid on. He scampers through to the other end, while Lahiru Kumara is struggling to get to his end, but he makes it at the end. Single taken!
Shorter now, around middle. Lahiru Kumara defends it out.
Quicker now, drifting it in, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella pushes it towards mid off.
Loopy ball, full, on middle. Niroshan Dickwella works it towards square leg.
Fuller, quick again, outside off. Niroshan Dickwella steps down and looks to go over cover but misses and gets hit on his back pad.
Full again, on middle. Niroshan Dickwella sweeps it towards square leg. No run there!
Tad fuller, spinning in around the leg pole. Niroshan Dickwella goes for the reverse-sweep but misses.
Fuller ball, around off. Niroshan Dickwella steps down and looks to heave this over the leg side, but he gets an inside edge onto his pads.
Loopy ball, around middle. Lahiru Kumara leans and defends it out.
Tad quicker, full again, on middle. Lahiru Kumara blocks it out.
Full again, on middle and leg. Lahiru Kumara defends and gets an outside edge past the first slip fielder.
Slower through the air, full, on middle. Lahiru Kumara blocks it out.
Loopy again, full, around off. Lahiru Kumara defends it out watchfully.
Loopy delivery, full, around off. Lahiru Kumara blocks it out. He survives the full over!
Quicker, on middle, fuller ball. Niroshan Dickwella steps down the pitch and pushes it back to the bowler.
Around middle and leg, fuller ball. Niroshan Dickwella pushes it towards mid-wicket.
Outside off, fuller ball. Niroshan Dickwella pushes it past cover for a single. Lahiru Kumara will be on strike! Fifty for Niroshan Dickwella! It has been a good inning from the wicket-keeper batter.
Fuller delivery, outside off. Lahiru Kumara blocks it out towards point.
Tosses it up, around off. Lahiru Kumara defends it out again.
FOUR! Lahiru Kumara gets off the mark in style! Tad shorter, around middle. Lahiru Kumara lifts it over mid on for a boundary!
Loopy ball, full, around off. Niroshan Dickwella defends it out.
Slower through the air, full and around middle. Niroshan Dickwella defends it out.
Down the leg side, full ball. Niroshan Dickwella sweeps it towards fine leg for a single.
In the air...but safe! A loopy ball, fuller in length. Lahiru Kumara leans and lifts it towards mid on, but the ball falls just short of Jasprit Bumrah there!
Outside off, blocked out.

OUT! CAUGHT! Ravichandran Ashwin finishes things off! He grabs his fourth wicket! A fuller ball, around middle. Lahiru Kumara stays in his crease and tries to go over long off, but the ball goes off the outer half of the bat towards mid off. Mohammed Shami runs forward and takes an easy catch. India win by an innings and 222 runs.
Howout: c Mohammed Shami b Ravichandran Ashwin
